2. **Bottlenecks**:
   - String splitting and tokenization is relatively expensive
   - Multiple string operations (getConnectionValue(), c_str() conversion)
   - Case-insensitive comparison requires per-character processing

3. **Optimization Opportunities**:
   - Avoid full tokenization if possible
   - Use direct string search first as fast path
   - Only do more expensive tokenization if needed
   - Consider common cases (exact match, simple comma-separated values)

4. **High-Impact Optimization Idea**:
   - First check for exact match (fast path)
   - Then check for simple comma-separated case (common case)
   - Only fall back to full tokenization if needed

